title: [New Beginnings]
description: Haphazard piles of assorted armor and weaponry lay scattered around the edges of the large canvas tent.  Thick modwir poles hold the awning aloft, and a thin mithril beam runs the length of the structure, strung with lanterns.  A banner depicting a boar's head is hung on the rear wall.
location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
